	   <a name=9692240813106></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f9692240813106><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj>Rogue Questions</span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Sep 17th 4:54 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am currently a low lvl rogue and I have a few questions that I would like answered if possible.<br>Is throwing a necessary skill? I think it might be and I think that I will also use a 1hs with piercing. How much damage does backstab auctually do at lvls. 10-20, 20-30, 30-40 and 40-50 and above. I currently have a dragoon dirk and I am working on a serrated bone dirk. Any help would be appreciated, thanks.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
	   </form></table><ul>
<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%>
	   <a name=9692244501990></a>
	   <form action=http://www1.allakhazam.com/perl/strategy/mrate.pl name=f9692244501990><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=2&mid=9692244501990>RE: Rogue Questions</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=2&mid=9692244501990#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Sep 17th 5:00 PM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.33]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>for throwing, it depends on what server you're on. on PvP, throwing is widely used by pure meleers because it interrupts spells better. rogues also get criticals (15 dmg with a shuriken) and deadly strikes (30 dmg) with throwing. these are nice little bonuses... although they don't compare to archery in terms of range and damage, many people choose throwing because it's cheaper, or because they like to roleplay their rogue. Still, i'd say archery would be preferred on a blue server.<br><br>at level 10, you'll start backstabbing for about 30 damage with your dragoon dirk. from there, your damage increases 1 damage point for every backstab skill point. you also backstab closer to your maximum when you have higher strength. increasing the damage of your weapon (ie upgrading to SBD, wise choice) will dramatically increase your maximum backstab. I'm level 29, and my max BS with an SBD is about 99, whereas my max with my burning rapier in primary (1 dmg point lower) is only in the 80s. <br><br>I hope this answers your questions, and good luck!<br><br>Kryven Cyclone &lt;Order of the Black Rose&gt;<br>29th season Assassin, Vallon Zek<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
